    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered like a member of the family. It's in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a speck of dust or a scratch in sight! If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is definitely the one. I\u2019m so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
