    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, and is entirely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows no wear or bolster creasing, and the original carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since new. Every electronic feature, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history from authorized dealerships and a whisper-quiet engine bay with zero leaks. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor. Includes both original keys and all owner manuals.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
