    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant, exhibiting optimal compression and a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile, precise shifts, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures linear power delivery. Crucially, the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains taut with no bushing deflection, and the original Laguna Seca Blue interior shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. This is a mechanically synchronized, turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
